Tamron/The Trainers

Tamron laughed as he saw the desperation in Spears.

"You hate this, don't you? Too bad. It's time to go see your new 
home."  At his point Tamron divided back into the original Trainers. 
Prebon continued with the talking.

"Savage, too me!(Savage came over to Prebon. He mounted him.) Spears, 
get on the back and hold your lover tight. We're going back to base. 
Anyone who follows will join Spears!"
